{"word":"Obed-Edom","slug":"obed-edom","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Obed-Edom</b> <a href=\"#/H5654\">H5654</a> <br/> 1. A Korhite Levite:<br/> - Doorkeeper of the ark<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=15&verse=18'>1Ch 15:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=15&verse=24'>1Ch 15:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=26&verse=8'>1Ch 26:8</a> <br/> - David leaves ark with<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=6&verse=10'>2Sa 6:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=13&verse=14'>1Ch 13:14</a> <br/> - Ark removed from<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=6&verse=12'>2Sa 6:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=15&verse=25'>1Ch 15:25</a> <br/> - Appointed to sound with harps<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=15&verse=21'>1Ch 15:21</a> <br/> - Appointed to minister before the ark<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=16&verse=5'>1Ch 16:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=16&verse=38'>1Ch 16:38</a> <br/> 2. A doorkeeper of the temple<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=16&verse=38'>1Ch 16:38</a><br/> 3. A conservator of the vessels of the temple in time of Amaziah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=25&verse=24'>2Ch 25:24</a>"}]}